{"tid":650081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：「正接受稅局調査不宜任政協副主席」屬嚴重誹謗","createTime":"2018-05-02T04:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T04:55:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec575acf7eeb8727610453f8814f8ea005c277f5","tid":650081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180502/s00001/348e84b0eceee859f43d2f49c5ba2f52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F348e84b0eceee859f43d2f49c5ba2f52.jpg&h=791e0d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英再於facebook談及UGL事件，今次點名要求會計界梁繼昌回應，會否收回對他的指控。梁振英早上於fb以＜請梁繼昌回應＞為題發帖，指對方去年3月1日在記者會上，説他正在接受香港及外國稅局的調査，不適宜出任全國政協副主席，形容是「嚴重的誹謗」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英強調「去年3月1日之前，以及在去年3月1日至今都沒有收過任何稅局的任何査詢，遑論調査」，要求梁繼昌公開收回指控，明言「梁繼昌對我這個要求回應不回應，如何回應，將來請法庭一併考慮」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英去年3月仍是香港特首時，已入稟高等法院控告梁繼昌誹謗。入稟狀指出，梁繼昌部分內容誹謗及破壞其聲譽，要求法庭頒禁制令，禁制梁繼昌及相關人士再以任何方式發布有關言論，並向梁繼昌索加重及懲罰性賠償，另要求梁繼昌支付訟費。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民主黨眾籌調查UGL事件，要求梁振英公開與UGL簽訂離職協議的相關文件，但梁振英日前透過fb發聲明，強調自己「沒有責任向任何其他人披露我和第三者的通信和會議紀錄」，重申保留追究誹謗權利。"},{"pid":"1d5f654b1e5fd6763e2f2d1ddd6833a09bc88909","tid":650081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180502/s00001/1525231093870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F1525231093870&d=nRHBUVZHhqwhhyqBOnRgtP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4ff04a6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F1525231093870&h=69ca1f67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180502/s00001/1525231093870</a>"},{"pid":"eeab75de6b291387d32dd1e8879b15abac524a60","tid":650081,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"fair comments 都可以告?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afe7d5b312bcf79e3f1d1f2540250ae0d8ef6bf","tid":650081,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重申保留追究誹謗權利</blockquote><br />\n係就快D出信唔係就收皮喇屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}